hackathon-description-text: 12 Hours of hacking at Saginaw Valley State University
hackathon-eligibility:
As long as you live local, you are welcome to come! 
Teams up to a maximum of four (4) people.
Unregistered hackers will not be allowed to participate.
Remote participation is not allowed.
